This [**solution**](https://leetcode.com/submissions/detail/819479897/) employs a functional-style approach to find and replace letters. It demonstrated **0 ms runtime (100.00%)** and used **2.0 MB memory (100.00%)**. Time complexity is linear: **O(N)**. Space complexity is linear: **O(N)**. Detailed comments are provided.

